definitions.definition: Likely to crunch , especially with reference to food when it is eaten.
examples: I put some lettuce in the burger to make it more crunchy .

definitions.definition: Having counter-culture sensibilities; nature-loving or hippie ; wholesome , health-conscious .
examples: San Francisco was a very crunchy town.
Silky mama won't typically go for cloth diapers like crunchy mama .

definitions.definition: Of a chord , containing dissonant intervals.
Of an image, pixelated , grainy , or exhibiting blocking , often as a result of oversharpening , a low resolution , or aggressively applied lossy image compression .

main_definition: Likely to crunch , especially with reference to food when it is eaten.
